---
title: Sweet-Soy Tofu & Beef Strip Stir Fry  with Garlic Rice & Asian Greens
description: You’ll be off to visit your happy place when you get a taste of this dish. Sweet with a touch of salt, that’s how we’re cooking up our tofu tonight, with a deliciously decadent stir-fry sauce and a buttery garlic rice with veggies to finish it off, we wish you safe travels to bliss.

